# GOCOS App

Global Ocean Contamination Open-Source Ecosystem — mobile/web application for
real-time marine PFAS and microplastics contamination monitoring, citizen
science observation reporting, and vessel tracking across the Caribbean,
Arctic, Baltic, and South Pacific.

Live app: https://gocos-app.vercel.app

## About

Developed by the Sustainable Seas Institute and the University of North
Carolina at Charlotte. Built on React, deployable to iOS, Android, and web.

## Data

Underlying scientific datasets are published openly on Zenodo, e.g.
https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.20262315

